title: One of our most desired floor plan! Near schools & shopping, 2BR apt
posting_body: ['Welcome Home To Tenzen.', 'Tenzen is a community that has been completely remodeled inside and out – with condominium level, upscale interiors.', 'Tenzen residents share a central courtyard in the trees, featuring a stunning fountain.', 'In addition, residents will find a central patio with grilling area, comfortable seating, and heaters (for chilly nights).', 'The Tenzen community is conveniently located for your car or your feet, easy access to I-90 and I-405 and just steps from shopping, restaurants, movies and services.', 'Imagine walking to the grocery store in a matter of minutes.', 'Give Us A Call… we’d love to show you your new home.', 'Call our leasing office!', 'This apartment features:', 'Enjoy BONUS Sun Room', 'Granite countertops', 'Stainless steel appliances', 'Convenient W/D', 'Large deck with extra storage', 'Wood burning fireplace', 'Garage Parking Available', 'Come Visit us!', 'Tenzen Apartments', '4117 124th Avenue Southeast', 'Bellevue, WA 98006', '<URL>', 'Contact us today to schedule a tour!', 'Call', 'show contact info', 'Office Hours: Tuesday - Saturday 9:00am – 6:00pm', 'Photos in ad may not be of actual apartment, however we try our best to use photos similar to the floor plan.']
